description: In this issue, our heroes travel through the Grandwood Forest seeking the Dragonhold, a magical item which may be able to save the city of Rel Astra from Blackwing and hisdragon siblings. But to reach the Dragonhold, two heroes must face their deepest secrets and darkest fears.
name: Part 5: Guardian of the Dragonhold

volume.name: Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons

description: After our heroes mind-bending journey through the mystical space containing the Dragonhold weapon, they meet an even deadlier obstacle... Azzre, the dragon-sibling of Blackwing and Eclipse! But Azzre does not come to do battle... he has come to deal secretly with the heroes, offering a solution they had not considered. But can a dragon's word be trusted? Must someone die before the mighty dragon Blackwing can be defeated? This issue also features the confrontation between the paladin Lucien and the convicted murderer Kiernan. Will either one walk away alive?
name: Part 6: An Eclipse of Stolen Blood

volume.name: Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons

description: This penultimate issue begins with the fearsome dragon Blackwing fast approaching the metropolis of Rel Astra. But Blackwing is not the only threat to the city... The greatest threat to the heroes lurks within their own group! Some will fight. Some will die. And one will betray them all.
name: Part 7: Wrapped in Betrayal's Kiss

volume.name: Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons

description: The stunning conclusion to the incredible saga! The heroes face not one, but two dangerous threats ? a fearsome dragon-attack and a murderous assault by one whom they formerly called friend. Death, betrayal, murder, and revenge... it's all here. But how will it end? The answer will surprise you!
name: Part 8: Where Strangers Once Stood...

volume.name: Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons

description: Abby has found a great guy: Mark has a steady job, good looks and a down-to-earth attitude. But, Mark has finally decided to let Abby in on his big secret: he is actually the beloved superhero The Crusader. Can Abby deal with Super-exes, keeping secrets and irregular schedules now that Mark has come clean?

It's wintertime, and Abby and Mark are keeping busy: a wedding, a canceled book signing and gift-getting anxiety have our Superguy and Not-quite-Super gal barely having time to enjoy the season. Will visiting their families give them the chance to enjoy the reason for the season or will it just result in more headaches?

Abby's sister, Charlotte, can't take it anymore: the Supercouple is starting to drive her Super-crazy. With Valentine's Day coming up, Abby thinks all that Charlotte needs is a date. Going online for her search, Charlotte runs into a guy that might just be who she is looking for. After all, what could go wrong when going on a date with a Super villian?

Mark is pretty worked up that the Arachnerd is getting a movie while the Crusader (his superhero persona) gets little attention. Abby tries to get his mind off it by taking a trip to a picnic with her family. Mark finally decides to extend a gracious hand to Arachnerd and Abby plans a big surprise for Mark... with a little help from the Liberty League.

With Abby's play and Mark's mom dropping into town, when's a Superhero supposed to get some free time with his lady? As more and more problems pile up, an undecipherable prophecy is given to the Crusader. Will he figure it out before it comes to pass?

When Amazonia picks Abby's bookstore as the place to hold her book signing, what could go wrong? Well... Tensions flare as Abby discovers that the book is more than a little revealing about Amazonia's past relationship with the Crusader (Mark's superhero persona). As she reads more and more about their Super-relationship, will it prove a fatal blow to her own relationship with Mark?

If you missed the Free Comic Book Day Edition, here's your chance to get it again, featuring a special new 'Major Might' cover. When last we left them, the Crusader was going to propose to his girlfriend Abby over Christmas. Sounds easy, right? Too bad nothing's ever easy when you're a super-hero! Check out comicdom's favorite super couple in the latest all new installment of the super-hero situation comedy!

Charlotte goes to Paris, leaving Abby to find a proper replacement. Mark and Abby go to a wedding fair - only to wind up at a comic book convention! And, where's Amazonia been? Find out in the latest installment of comicdom's favorite superhero-romance-comedy!

The Crusader's been replaced by Psi-Clone and the evil duplicate is causing all sorts of problems for Deco City's resident superhero. Can the real Crusader return before the fake causes too much damage - especially to his relationships with Abby and Amazonia? Plus, more wedding plan fun, and Abby comes to a major realization. All this and more in the latest installment of comicdom's favorite superhero sitcom!

Abby and Amazonia... friends?! It's the most shocking issue of Love and Capes ever! What could cause these two women to suddenly become BFFs? Plus, Abby's quest for her dress continues, and their parents finally meet! Don't miss the last issue before the big wedding in LNC #12!

It's the event that every fan of Love and Capes has been awaiting with baited breath - the wedding of Abby and the Crusader. The superheroic soap opera reaches a crescendo in this 48 page double issue!
Mid Ohio-Con and Baltimore Comic-Con exclusives.

Dungeons & Dragons is the most popular role-playing game ever. Now, D&D returns to comics and wastes no time in wreaking havoc upon the hapless citizens of Rel Astra within the world of Greyhawk. Three powerful dragons come in search of a treasure that Rel Astra must give up or the dragons will decimate every living creature within the metropolis. There is a problem; Rel Astra doesn't have it! Four brave souls are charged with the responsibility of finding what the dragons seek before their home is burned to the ground. Can these heroes save their people in time when they do not even know what they are searching for?
name: Part 1: The Last of My Father

volume.name: Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons
Dungeons And Dragons: In The Shadow Of Dragons

description: The conclusion to what's sure to be the most talked about book of the year! Boarding a gigantic luxury liner to take over wasn't supposed to be so hard especially with only four thousand flesh hungry zombies on the loose. What will be the fate of our nine survivors on board, and will anybody be alive when it's all over to care!?
name: Belly of the Worm

description:
Imagine a world where equally populated by mystical gurus, urban hipsters, and dark forces bent on tipping our drab mundane world into the shadows.

Modeled after Joseph Campbell's Hero Cycle, Nox is a post modern road trip adventure and urban fantasy that explores normal people in fantastic situations and asks the question : Would you cross the threshold?

name: LES GUÉRILLEROS
MISSION À L'EST
ÇA CHAUFFE AU PÔLE
LA HAVANE, ALLER ET RETOUR
LA GRANDE LESSIVE
